column1: TITLE: Physical variables - lake profile additional logger system from Feresjön

COMMENTS: Deployed O2 (Dissolved Oxygen) sensors @-1 and @-10m. O2 calculated based on Garcia and Gordon (1992): https://doi.org/10.4319/lo.1992.37.6.1307. Due to an error in the original calculation of O2_-10m
column2: all values have been replaced with NaNs. O2_-10m data from any previously downloaded versions of this dataset should not be used.

column1: O2_-1m - Dissolved Oxygen (mg L-1). Aanderaa optode @-1m. Calculated based on [O2SAT_-1m] and [TW_O2_-1m]. 30 min average from 2 min readings.
O2SAT_-1m - Oxygen saturation (%) Aanderaa optode @-1m. 30 min average from 2 min readings.
TW_O2_-1m - Water temperature (°C). Aanderaa optode @-1m. 30 min average from 2 min readings.
O2_-10m - Dissolved Oxygen (mg L-1). Aanderaa optode @-10m. Calculated based on [O2SAT_-10m] and [TW_O2_-10m]. 30 min average from 2 min readings.
O2SAT_-10m - Oxygen saturation (%) Aanderaa optode @-10m. 30 min average from 2 min readings.
TW_O2_-10m - Water temperature (°C). Aanderaa optode @-10m. 30 min average from 2 min readings.
